## рҹ“Ҳ Performance Benchmarks

### Expected Model Performance (on sample data)

| Model | Test RВІ | Test RMSE | Test MAE |
|-------|---------|-----------|----------|
| Linear Regression | 0.70 | 8.89 | 6.78 |
| Random Forest | 0.82 | 6.78 | 5.12 |
| **AI-Enhanced (Gradient Boosting)** | **0.88** | **5.34** | **4.12** |

### System Requirements

- **Minimum**: 4GB RAM, 2 CPU cores
- **Recommended**: 8GB RAM, 4 CPU cores
- **Storage**: 2GB for data and models

